<p>The renovations are finished! This generator is almost entirely JavaScript. <b>Known issues:</b><br>
- A bunch of words (like <i>sallonu</i>) are mistakenly set to be indirect objects of some verbs (i.e "She is hitting on behalf of the shoreline"). This is not supposed to be the case. Please tell me if you see one of these words being the indirect object like that.<br>
  If you encounter any issues, please let me know on the Adamantine's Drainbox thread of the <a href="https://yongasabi.freeforums.net/">Yongasabi Forums</a>.
</p>

<p>By the way, the <b><a href="https://perchance.org/yongasabi-verb-tenses-training">Verb Tenses Training Generator</a></b> is mostly finished and can use every case marker! Go give it a whirl!</p>

